data.description: Welcome to 290 Winona Ave, Washington PA! Located in the Trinity Area School District! Move-In Ready!! All Brick Ranch on a Beautiful Lot with Mature Trees. A Cozy Sunporch welcomes you into this Lovely home with a Large Living Room! All Appliances stay in the Eat-In Kitchen. Hardwood floors under the carpet in Living Room & Bedrooms! Recently updated Full Bathroom! A Nice Breezeway takes you to the 1-Car Garage. Huge Unfinished Basement with So Much Potential! There's also a nice Covered Patio off the back of home to enjoy a morning cup of coffee/tea! Walking distance to Trinity High School, Close to the food and entertainment in downtown Washington!! Also conveniently located close to 70 & 79 for an Easy Commute!
